    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/77e9b6110d4e6cd8b72223150dfd5a7c.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/77e9b6110d4e6cd8b72223150dfd5a7c.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/77e9b6110d4e6cd8b72223150dfd5a7c.mp4?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >道路并不平坦：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏挑战着每一位玩家！不要放弃！输得越多，你就会变得越强！</strong><br>你喜欢樱花？- 不客气 如果你喜欢艺术，这里有！你喜欢思考谜题？- 这里有数不清的谜题！你喜欢 BOSS 战？- 这里有好几个！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏共有 100 个关卡和几个秘密关卡！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/40c2f459a1d1cfeef42329c9b4ab2c6a.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/40c2f459a1d1cfeef42329c9b4ab2c6a.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/40c2f459a1d1cfeef42329c9b4ab2c6a.mp4?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有趣的机制不会让您感到无聊</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种谜题</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>整个游戏是黑白的</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有些关卡你可以甚至需要放松一下</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/8153ef5f88235bb692ca7048eb966b3c.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=715 height=343 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/8153ef5f88235bb692ca7048eb966b3c.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Bleb 与女友分手后，他陷入了一个梦境，现在他要面对很多挑战！但之后会发生什么呢？</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/a1a8fe51246200297c926a4aef173d66.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/a1a8fe51246200297c926a4aef173d66.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于开发者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这款游戏是由一位独立开发者制作的。</strong><i>“我想制作一款游戏，让玩家在完成每个关卡后都能说--哦，是的，我成功了！”</i></p>",
